In this webinar, VentureCrowd CEO Steve Maarbani talks to VentureCrowd Development Manager Neil Walker about how equity investors target 25% to 35% ROE on property development projects and explains the financial feasibility for VentureCrowd’s Park Ridge project in detail.</h2>
                            
